                    <!-- page 1 -->
                    <cbml:panel n="1">
                        <cbml:caption type="heading">
                            <emph rendition="#b">Chapter one   The Map</emph>
                            <emph FBL="Logo">bone logo in top left corner</emph>
                        </cbml:caption>
                        <note type="pageDesc"> Smiley and Phoney, along with Fone Bone being kicked out into the desert
                        </note>
                    </cbml:panel>
                    
                    <cbml:panel n="2" characters="#FB #SB #PB">
                        <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#FB"> Still no sign of the townspeople. </cbml:balloon>
                        <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#SB"> HEY! Ya hear that Phoney? Th’ coast is clear! </cbml:balloon>
                        <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#SB"> Look at him! We got chased outta Boneville over two weeks ago, an’ he’s still mopin’ around! </cbml:balloon>
                        <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#SB"> …Oh, well… I guess you can whine all you want, when yer th’ richest guy in th’ whole town. </cbml:balloon>
                        <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#SB"> Oops! Silly me. Ex-richest! </cbml:balloon>
                        <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#PB"> AAAH! </cbml:balloon>
                        <note type="panelDesc"> character dialogues </note>
                    </cbml:panel>
                    
                    <!-- page 2 -->
                    <cbml:panel n="1">
                        <cbml:caption type="heading">
                            <emph rendition="#b">Out from Boneville</emph>
                        </cbml:caption>
                        <note type="pageDesc"> all three are agruing</note>
                    </cbml:panel>
                    
                    <cbml:panel n="2" characters="#FB #PB">
                        <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#FB"> Don’t get him started. </cbml:balloon>
                        <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#PB"> They can’t do this to me! You can’t do anything to a rich person that he doesn’t want! </cbml:balloon>
                        <note type="panelDesc"> character dialogues </note>
                    </cbml:panel>
                    
                    <cbml:panel n="3" characters="#PB">
                        <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#PB"> GASP! OH! Th’ horrible injustice of it all! I’m still reeling with shock!! </cbml:balloon>
                        <note type="panelDesc"> character dialogues </note>
                    </cbml:panel>
                    
                    <cbml:panel n="4" characters="#PB">
                        <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#PB"> I’m a respected community leader! A shining pillar of moral strength! </cbml:balloon>
                        <note type="panelDesc"> character dialogues </note>
                    </cbml:panel>
                    
                    <cbml:panel n="5" characters="#PB">
                        <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#PB"> …so a couple of shady business deals went sour…is THAT any reason to run th’ most beloved bone in Boneville out on a rail?! </cbml:balloon>
                        <note type="panelDesc"> character dialogues </note>
                    </cbml:panel>
                    
                    <cbml:panel n="6" characters="#FB">
                        <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#FB"> Yes. </cbml:balloon>
                        <note type="panelDesc"> character dialogues </note>
                    </cbml:panel>
                    
                    <cbml:panel n="6" characters="#SB">
                        <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#SB"> Beloved? Th’ mayor declared a school holiday just so th’ kids could come and throw ROCKS at you! </cbml:balloon>
                        <note type="panelDesc"> character dialogues </note>
                    </cbml:panel>
                    
                    <cbml:panel n="7" characters="#PB">
                        <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#PB"> Ingrates! Oh, they’ll RUE th’ day they chased PHONCIBLE P. BONE outta their crumb ol’ town! *sniff!* </cbml:balloon>
                        <note type="panelDesc"> character dialogues </note>
                    </cbml:panel>
                    
                    <cbml:panel n="8" characters="#SB">
                        <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#SB"> Now, now, little buckaroo! Don’t be sad! It’s a beautiful day! There’s not a cloud in th’ sky! </cbml:balloon>
                        <note type="panelDesc"> character dialogues </note>
                    </cbml:panel>
                    
                    <!-- page 3 -->
                    <cbml:panel n="1">
                        <cbml:caption type="heading">
                            <emph rendition="#b">The Map</emph>
                        </cbml:caption>
                        <note type="pageDesc"> all three are agruing still</note>
                    </cbml:panel>
                    
                    <cbml:panel n="2" characters="#FB #SB">
                        <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#FB"> Good point, Smiley. If we don’t find some shade soon, I’m gonna have a stroke! </cbml:balloon>
                        <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#SB"> Hey, I’m just tryin’ to cheer him up, okay? (Indicate whispering for this balloon) </cbml:balloon>
                        <note type="panelDesc"> character dialogues </note>
                    </cbml:panel>
                    
                    <cbml:panel n="3" characters="#SB">
                        <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#SB"> Try thinkin’ about somethin’ besides your money! </cbml:balloon>
                        <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#SB"> Take me for example! I never had a penny in my life! </cbml:balloon>
                        <note type="panelDesc"> character dialogues </note>
                    </cbml:panel>
                    
                    <cbml:panel n="4" characters="#SB #PB">
                        <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#SB"> But I’m not sad! I got no responsibilities! I’m free! Free as a BIRD! </cbml:balloon>
                        <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#PB"> A Bird? Ha! More like a mangy, stray dog who doesn’t eat very often! </cbml:balloon>
                        <note type="panelDesc"> character dialogues </note>
                    </cbml:panel>
                    
                    <cbml:panel n="5" characters="#SB #PB">
                        <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#SB"> Well… true! But you get my point! </cbml:balloon>
                        <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#FB"> HEY! FONE BONE! </cbml:balloon>
                        <note type="panelDesc"> character dialogues </note>
                    </cbml:panel>
                    
                    <cbml:panel n="6" characters="#FB #PB">
                        <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#FB"> What? </cbml:balloon>
                        <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#PB"> Have you figured out where we are, yet? What’s takin’ so long? </cbml:balloon>
                        <note type="panelDesc"> character dialogues </note>
                    </cbml:panel>
                    
                    <cbml:panel n="7" characters="#FB">
                        <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#FB"> I’m working on it. Hmmmm….That’s strange…that mountain range isn’t on any of my charts— </cbml:balloon>
                        <note type="panelDesc"> character dialogues </note>
                    </cbml:panel>
                    
                    <!-- page 4 -->
                    <cbml:panel n="1">
                        <cbml:caption type="heading">
                            <emph rendition="#b">Out From Boneville</emph>
                        </cbml:caption>
                        <note type="pageDesc"> all three are agruing still</note>
                    </cbml:panel>
                    
                    <cbml:panel n="2" characters="#FB #PB">
                        <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#FB"> Hey - - ! </cbml:balloon>
                        <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#PB"> Lemme see that! </cbml:balloon>
                        <note type="panelDesc"> character dialogues </note>
                    </cbml:panel>
                    
                    <cbml:panel n="3" characters="#PB">
                        <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#PB"> Here's your problem Fone Bone! We're off the map! Get a bigger Map! </cbml:balloon>
                        <note type="panelDesc"> character dialogues </note>
                    </cbml:panel>
                    
                    <cbml:panel n="4" characters="#PB #FB">
                        <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#FB"> That's as big as maps get! We're in uncharted territory! </cbml:balloon>
                        <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#PB"> Well get us back! </cbml:balloon>
                        <note type="panelDesc"> character dialogues </note>
                    </cbml:panel>
                    
                    <cbml:panel n="5" characters="#PB #FB #SM">
                        <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#FB"> I can't! We're lost! </cbml:balloon>
                        <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#SB"> To boldly go where no bone has gone before! </cbml:balloon>
                        <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#PB"> Stick a sock in it, cabbage head! </cbml:balloon>
                        <note type="panelDesc"> character dialogues </note>
                    </cbml:panel>
                    
                    <cbml:panel n="6" characters="#PB">
                        <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#PB"> Don't get me wrong fone bone -- I'm grateful you were able to et me outta town -- but tell me ... why did you hafta go an' bring him with us? </cbml:balloon>
                        <note type="panelDesc"> character dialogues </note>
                    </cbml:panel>
                    
                    <cbml:panel n="7" characters="#PB #FB #SM">
                        <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#PB"> To torture you. </cbml:balloon>
                        <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#PB"> I KNEW THAT! </cbml:balloon>
                        <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#PB"> Hey, Phoney! Bad news ... we're out of water! </cbml:balloon>
                        <note type="panelDesc"> character dialogues </note>
                    </cbml:panel>
                    
                    <!-- page 5 -->
                    <cbml:panel n="1">
                        <cbml:caption type="heading">
                            <emph rendition="#b">The Map</emph>
                        </cbml:caption>
                        <note type="pageDesc"> all three are agruing still</note>
                    </cbml:panel>
                    
                    <cbml:panel n="2" characters="#PB #FB #SB">
                        <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#PB"> THAT'S THE LAST STRAW! </cbml:balloon>
                        <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#FB"> Don't get mad at smily bone! This mess isn't his fault! </cbml:balloon>
                        <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#SB"> That's right! Th' townspeople aren't mad at us! They ran you outta town 'cause you're a selfish, little greedbag! </cbml:balloon>
                        <note type="panelDesc"> character dialogues </note>
                    </cbml:panel>
                    
                    <cbml:panel n="3" characters="#PB #FB">
                        <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#PB"> I can't believe it! Not only am I broke -- now i'm gonna die broke! Gasp! Coff! Coff! </cbml:balloon>
                        <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#FB"> Oh, you're not gonna die! I just hope you learned your lesson! </cbml:balloon>
                        <note type="panelDesc"> character dialogues </note>
                    </cbml:panel>
                    
                    <cbml:panel n="4" characters="#PB #FB #SB">
                        <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#PB"> Water! I need water! I can feel my tongue crackling! </cbml:balloon>
                        <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#SB"> Hey, cousins , look what I found! I think it's a map! </cbml:balloon>
                        <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#FB"> ?! </cbml:balloon>
                        <note type="panelDesc"> character dialogues </note>
                    </cbml:panel>
                    
                    <cbml:panel n="5" characters="#PB #SB">
                        <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#SB"> Sure enough! Look! It's a map of that mountain range! </cbml:balloon>
                        <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#PB"> I'm saved! Give it to me! </cbml:balloon>
                        <note type="panelDesc"> character dialogues </note>
                    </cbml:panel>
                    
                    <cbml:panel n="6" characters="#PB #FB #SB">
                        <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#SB"> Gimme a dollar first. </cbml:balloon>
                        <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#PB"> What? </cbml:balloon>
                        <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#FB"> Go on, Phoney give him a dollar! </cbml:balloon>
                        <note type="panelDesc"> character dialogues </note>
                    </cbml:panel>
                    
                    <cbml:panel n="4" characters="#PB #FB">
                        <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#PB"> WHAT?! </cbml:balloon>
                        <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#FB"> We're lost in the middle of th' desert! Give him a dollar! </cbml:balloon>
                        <note type="panelDesc"> character dialogues </note>
                    </cbml:panel>
                    
                    <!-- page number 21 -->
                    <cbml:panel n="1">
                        <cbml:caption type="heading">
                            <emph rendition="#b">The Map</emph>
                        </cbml:caption>
                        <note type="pageDesc"> Fone Bone and Ted Ted are waling through the forest
                        </note>
                    </cbml:panel>

                    <cbml:panel n="2" characters="#FB #TT #RC">
                        <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#FB"> Where can I get something to drink?
                            I’m dyin’ of thirst! </cbml:balloon>
                        <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#TT"> We can stop by th’ Barrelhaven! They
                            brews th’ best stuff aroun’! </cbml:balloon>
                        <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#RC"> Eh? </cbml:balloon>
                        <note type="panelDesc"> character dialogues </note>
                    </cbml:panel>

                    <cbml:panel n="3" characters=" #FB #TT #RC">
                        <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#RC"> Comrade! We are about to feast!
                            Quick! Get your fast carcass behind this bush and get ready! </cbml:balloon>
                        <note type="panelDesc"> Rat Creature talking to Fone Bone </note>
                    </cbml:panel>

                    <cbml:panel n="4" characters="#FB #TT #RC">
                        <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#RC"> Hello, small mammal….could you step
                            in here for a moment? I’ve got something to show you…. </cbml:balloon>
                        <note type="panelDesc"> Rat Creature talking to Fone Bone </note>
                    </cbml:panel>


                    <cbml:panel n="5" characters="#FB #TT #RC">
                        <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#FB"> Can’t you show me out here where I’ve
                            got runnin’ space? </cbml:balloon>
                        <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#RC"> No! No! Please! Step in here— your
                            friend the dragon isn’t around, is he? </cbml:balloon>
                        <note type="panelDesc"> Fone Bone and Rat Creature talking </note>
                    </cbml:panel>

                    <cbml:panel n="6" characters="#FB #TT #RC1 #RC2">
                        <cbml:balloon rendition="#jaggies" type="speech" who="#FB"> Hey, Ted! Where
                            you goin’? </cbml:balloon>
                        <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#TT"> You’re on yer own Bone! </cbml:balloon>
                        <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#RC1"> Quick, Comrade! Start the cooking
                            fire! </cbml:balloon>
                        <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#RC2"> No. You called me fat. </cbml:balloon>
                        <note type="panelDesc"> Two rat creatures talking with Fone Bone and Ted Ted
                        </note>
                    </cbml:panel>


                </div>
            </div>
